Lemon Cherry Gelato


Behold, THE Lemon Cherry Gelato - a luscious hybrid strain that crosses GSC and Sunset Sherbet to create a one-of-a-kind experience. Its aroma is a delightful bouquet of zesty lemon and sweet cherry, with subtle earthy undertones. The Limonene terpene content provides a refreshing citrusy flavor that awakens your senses, while its effects deliver a perfect balance of relaxation and euphoria. Indulge in this fragrant and delicious strain - a true masterpiece of nature.


Phenotype

Hybrid


Cross

GSC x Sunset Sherbert


Notes

Meyer lemons, Amarena Cherries, Hibiscus


Vape

1g & 5g Vape Cartridge


Bloom 510 cartridges are made of quality glass and ceramic parts fully customized to the high terpene content of our oil. Offering smooth hits from start to finish. Available in .5g and 1g sizes for Bloom Classic and Bloom Live. Battery sold separately.


The Bloom Battery is a sleek, buttonless battery tailored to heat Bloom’s oil at the perfect temperature, ensuring you never damage the terpenes or their flavor. Breath-activated and conveniently charged using a USB plug, the Bloom Battery is compatible with .5g and 1g cartridges (standard 510 thread).
